QuestData.Title: Shark Weak
QuestData.Description: That's one tough shark!$b$bYou determine that it's in everyone's best interest to try and distract Budd and hope his attention never returns to Gnaws and this Skeletal Reef.$b$bPerhaps the teeth of the beast will prove captivating enough...
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect 5 of Gnaws' teeth from the Skeletal Reef.
QuestData.RewardText: What?!$b$bGnaws ain't dead?!$b$bThis kinda takes the quick outta my get rich quick scheme...$b$bThem giant shark teeth are nice and all, but we can't stop 'til that shiney is ours!
